850
00:31:19,280 --> 00:31:20,920
That's just how Xin Ran sees it.

851
00:31:21,080 --> 00:31:23,080
She can't tie you to Dayazhai

852
00:31:23,080 --> 00:31:24,160
and never let go, can she?

853
00:31:25,640 --> 00:31:27,600
It's a non-exclusive contract, Xuan Yan.

854
00:31:28,040 --> 00:31:29,040
They handle online,

855
00:31:29,040 --> 00:31:30,040
we handle offline.

856
00:31:30,440 --> 00:31:31,520
Why wouldn't it work?

857
00:31:31,800 --> 00:31:33,280
That's how you see it,

858
00:31:33,280 --> 00:31:34,760
but Xin Ran doesn't see it that way.

859
00:31:35,240 --> 00:31:37,760
Whether it's for Xin Ran's sake or mine,

860
00:31:37,920 --> 00:31:39,840
I need to have a talk with Zheng Guohui,

861
00:31:39,880 --> 00:31:41,440
and see if he's willing to cooperate.

862
00:31:41,960 --> 00:31:44,200
After all, for me, Dayazhai

863
00:31:44,800 --> 00:31:46,120
was the one who gave me my start.

864
00:31:46,880 --> 00:31:49,400
Even if I give up some profit,

865
00:31:49,920 --> 00:31:51,040
that's perfectly fine.

866
00:31:56,520 --> 00:31:58,320
I owe them big for recognizing my worth.

867
00:31:58,960 --> 00:32:01,040
You're going all-in on loyalty, huh?

868
00:32:03,120 --> 00:32:04,720
Fine, I respect that.

869
00:32:05,320 --> 00:32:06,120
Oh, right.

870
00:32:06,120 --> 00:32:07,600
Director Liao also mentioned

871
00:32:07,640 --> 00:32:08,600
he wants me to organize

872
00:32:08,600 --> 00:32:10,160
the Xuan paper mill bosses and workers

873
00:32:10,160 --> 00:32:11,720
