877
00:32:18,880 --> 00:32:20,040
It's a perfect match.

878
00:32:20,040 --> 00:32:20,840
Absolutely fits.

879
00:32:21,720 --> 00:32:23,120
As long as the paper stands, we stand.

880
00:32:24,040 --> 00:32:25,120
Nice words, but...

881
00:32:26,440 --> 00:32:27,640
this paper dragon boat of yours,

882
00:32:27,880 --> 00:32:29,280
is it actually reliable?

883
00:32:29,280 --> 00:32:30,560
Don't let us get on it

884
00:32:30,600 --> 00:32:31,320
