885
00:32:31,560 --> 00:32:32,800
It's made of paper after all.

886
00:32:32,800 --> 00:32:34,320
Don't let us all end up in the water.

887
00:32:34,320 --> 00:32:34,920
That'd be so embarrassing.

888
00:32:34,920 --> 00:32:35,960
If you don't get it, quit asking.

889
00:32:35,960 --> 00:32:37,320
Just follow the plan.

890
00:32:37,920 --> 00:32:40,120
This is science, materials science.

891
00:32:40,800 --> 00:32:41,640
Hurry up and eat.

892
00:32:41,880 --> 00:32:42,920
We've got work to do after this.

893
00:32:43,120 --> 00:32:45,360
Pre-orders for our Cosmic Voyage series,

894
00:32:45,360 --> 00:32:47,640
compared to our previous two series,

895
00:32:47,640 --> 00:32:49,320
have grown by 230 percent.

896
00:32:49,680 --> 00:32:52,200
Whether through online distributor channels

897
00:32:52,200 --> 00:32:54,120
or retail sales channels,

898
00:32:54,120 --> 00:32:56,480
both are showing rapid growth trends.

899
00:32:56,560 --> 00:32:58,640
I predict this year's performance

900
00:32:58,640 --> 00:33:00,480
will more than double our targets.

901
00:33:03,560 --> 00:33:05,320
There's an old Chinese saying:

902
00:33:05,320 --> 00:33:07,360
"Don't boast in victory, don't despair in defeat."

903
00:33:07,960 --> 00:33:08,760
Well done.

904
00:33:08,760 --> 00:33:11,200
We've achieved some results,

905
00:33:11,680 --> 00:33:12,960
but I still think

906
00:33:13,400 --> 00:33:15,640
in the vast market of Xuan paper

907
00:33:15,640 --> 00:33:17,360
cultural creative products,

908
00:33:17,600 --> 00:33:19,280
we're falling far short.

909
00:33:19,360 --> 00:33:20,800
I suggest everyone

910
00:33:20,840 --> 00:33:22,520
put in real effort on marketing,

911
00:33:22,520 --> 00:33:24,600
effort, more effort,

912
00:33:24,600 --> 00:33:25,600
and even more effort.

913
00:33:25,600 --> 00:33:28,120
Dig deep into the market's potential.

914
00:33:28,120 --> 00:33:29,600
Dare to break out of our niche.

915
00:33:29,600 --> 00:33:30,800
We need ambition,

916
00:33:30,800 --> 00:33:33,280
the guts to build nationwide collectibles,

917
00:33:33,400 --> 00:33:35,640
the guts to build phenomenal IP brands.

918
00:33:35,640 --> 00:33:37,680
That's what real ambition means.

919
00:33:43,400 --> 00:33:44,880
The Chairman's words

920
00:33:44,880 --> 00:33:46,600
are truly enlightening.

921
00:33:46,760 --> 00:33:48,280
Truly visionary.

922
00:33:48,280 --> 00:33:50,520
The whole vision is elevated.

923
00:33:51,120 --> 00:33:51,920
Chairman,

924
00:33:51,920 --> 00:33:53,480
I suggest we consider

925
00:33:53,480 --> 00:33:54,680
developing physical stores.

926
00:33:56,080 --> 00:33:58,200
Xuan paper cultural products are new.

927
00:33:58,200 --> 00:34:00,560
Physical stores can offer consumers

928
00:34:00,560 --> 00:34:02,600
an immersive experience.

929
00:34:02,680 --> 00:34:04,760
More precise traffic acquisition,

930
00:34:04,760 --> 00:34:07,120
high conversion, high-value services.

931
00:34:07,360 --> 00:34:09,480
These are all advantages of physical stores.

932
00:34:09,800 --> 00:34:12,320
This way, online and offline,

933
00:34:12,320 --> 00:34:13,600
we fire on both fronts.

934
00:34:13,600 --> 00:34:14,199
I believe

935
00:34:14,199 --> 00:34:16,800
for rapidly expanding the cultural product market,

936
00:34:16,800 --> 00:34:18,280
this offers huge benefits.

937
00:34:21,199 --> 00:34:22,199
Mr. Xuan,

938
00:34:23,000 --> 00:34:25,920
Online platforms have long since crushed

939
00:34:25,920 --> 00:34:28,520
brick-and-mortar stores completely.

940
00:34:28,600 --> 00:34:30,800
How can you have such an outdated idea?

941
00:34:30,880 --> 00:34:32,159
No, no, no, Chairman.

942
00:34:32,239 --> 00:34:33,880
Trendy figurines are different.

943
00:34:33,880 --> 00:34:37,320
We need consumers to have

944
00:34:37,639 --> 00:34:41,120
direct understanding and precise reach for Xuan paper products.

945
00:34:41,120 --> 00:34:43,159
We set up physical stores in

946
00:34:43,280 --> 00:34:44,800
commercial complexes

947
00:34:45,000 --> 00:34:46,400
where young people gather.

948
00:34:46,480 --> 00:34:48,840
The offline spread rate

949
00:34:48,840 --> 00:34:50,159
would be beyond imagination.

950
00:34:50,159 --> 00:34:53,199
You plan to set up stores

951
00:34:53,360 --> 00:34:54,600
in commercial complexes?

952
00:34:55,000 --> 00:34:56,560
The rent would be so expensive.

953
00:34:56,560 --> 00:34:58,160
Isn't the cost too high?

954
00:34:58,680 --> 00:35:01,120
Physical stores obviously cost more.

955
00:35:01,360 --> 00:35:03,680
But if we want to achieve

956
00:35:03,680 --> 00:35:06,120
the breakout the Chairman wants,

957
00:35:06,320 --> 00:35:08,120
we need three to five stores

958
00:35:08,120 --> 00:35:10,000
in first-tier cities initially.

959
00:35:10,280 --> 00:35:11,200
Once the model succeeds,

960
00:35:11,200 --> 00:35:13,920
we'll quickly replicate it

961
00:35:13,920 --> 00:35:14,920
in other first and second-tier cities.

962
00:35:15,200 --> 00:35:17,240
Young man, let me remind you,

963
00:35:17,240 --> 00:35:18,320
