967
00:35:24,880 --> 00:35:25,880
Why not stick with that?

968
00:35:25,880 --> 00:35:28,480
Why spend a huge investment

969
00:35:28,480 --> 00:35:30,120
on going offline?

970
00:35:30,120 --> 00:35:33,200
Aren't you out of your mind?

971
00:35:33,680 --> 00:35:34,480
Vice President Zhang,

972
00:35:35,080 --> 00:35:36,720
