973
00:35:36,720 --> 00:35:38,680
No need for personal attacks.

974
00:35:40,440 --> 00:35:41,400
Stop arguing.

975
00:35:43,040 --> 00:35:46,280
The company abandoned offline ten years ago.

976
00:35:46,280 --> 00:35:47,880
We won't backtrack.

977
00:35:50,480 --> 00:35:51,720
In that case,

978
00:35:52,480 --> 00:35:53,920
I have another proposal.

979
00:35:54,320 --> 00:35:56,040
My Kuandu Studio

980
00:35:56,040 --> 00:35:58,440
and Taohua Town Xuan Paper Association

981
00:35:58,440 --> 00:36:00,080
would jointly form a cooperative.

982
00:36:00,280 --> 00:36:01,800
We would invest

983
00:36:02,080 --> 00:36:03,480
to develop the offline market.

984
00:36:03,640 --> 00:36:05,360
Dayazhai wouldn't need to invest.

985
00:36:05,520 --> 00:36:07,760
You all heard him, right?

986
00:36:07,760 --> 00:36:09,720
Now his true colors are showing.

987
00:36:09,720 --> 00:36:10,520
His wings are hardened now,

988
00:36:10,520 --> 00:36:12,120
planning to go solo.

989
00:36:12,280 --> 00:36:13,800
Vice President Zhang, your mouth is really

990
00:36:14,760 --> 00:36:15,800
too chatty.

991
00:36:16,160 --> 00:36:17,800
Can't you let me finish?

992
00:36:24,480 --> 00:36:25,320
Everyone,

993
00:36:25,720 --> 00:36:26,800
no matter when,

994
00:36:27,080 --> 00:36:28,200
I will never forget

995
00:36:28,200 --> 00:36:30,080
Dayazhai's kindness in recognizing my worth.

996
00:36:30,440 --> 00:36:31,480
If Dayazhai

997
00:36:31,880 --> 00:36:34,200
is willing to invest offline,

998
00:36:34,440 --> 00:36:35,880
then everything stays as before,

999
00:36:35,920 --> 00:36:37,160
with Dayazhai leading.

1000
00:36:37,400 --> 00:36:39,480
If not, that's fine too.

1001
00:36:39,720 --> 00:36:41,240
From my personal share,

1002
00:36:41,240 --> 00:36:43,680
I'll give Dayazhai a 10% stake.

1003
00:36:44,280 --> 00:36:45,040
I believe

1004
00:36:45,200 --> 00:36:46,520
through our joint efforts,

1005
00:36:46,520 --> 00:36:49,400
we'll take the Xuan paper cultural market

1006
00:36:49,400 --> 00:36:50,800
to a new height,

1007
00:36:50,840 --> 00:36:51,960
achieving a win-win.

1008
00:36:52,680 --> 00:36:53,600
Mr. Xuan,

1009
00:36:53,840 --> 00:36:55,440
you're just too young.

1010
00:36:55,440 --> 00:36:57,840
Let me be even more blunt with you.

1011
00:36:57,840 --> 00:36:59,000
The Chairman means

1012
00:36:59,000 --> 00:37:02,480
you need to fully execute his intentions.

1013
00:37:02,600 --> 00:37:04,080
Whatever ideas you have now,

1014
00:37:04,080 --> 00:37:05,240
in his eyes,

1015
00:37:05,240 --> 00:37:06,360
are nothing at all.

1016
00:37:15,160 --> 00:37:16,200
Mr. Xuan.

1017
00:37:19,400 --> 00:37:20,160
You...

1018
00:37:24,600 --> 00:37:27,200
You're a fearless rookie, aren't you?

1019
00:37:27,320 --> 00:37:28,600
You're not a businessperson.

1020
00:37:29,080 --> 00:37:31,280
Know what drives a businessperson?

1021
00:37:31,920 --> 00:37:32,720
Profit.

1022
00:37:32,720 --> 00:37:34,360
You need to know who you are,

1023
00:37:34,360 --> 00:37:36,520
what you can and can't do.

1024
00:37:36,520 --> 00:37:37,360
Understand?

1025
00:37:39,920 --> 00:37:41,320
So what the Chairman means is,

1026
00:37:46,880 --> 00:37:47,880
no matter who it is,

1027
00:37:50,520 --> 00:37:51,400
on this offline matter,

1028
00:37:51,400 --> 00:37:53,080
he will never agree to it.

1029
00:37:57,000 --> 00:37:57,880
Why is that?

1030
00:38:07,200 --> 00:38:08,800
Does anyone else have questions?

1031
00:38:15,360 --> 00:38:16,200
No.

1032
00:38:17,480 --> 00:38:18,280
Chairman,

1033
00:38:18,680 --> 00:38:20,360
I don't think you have the right to refuse.

1034
00:38:20,520 --> 00:38:21,360
Xuan Yan.

1035
00:38:22,320 --> 00:38:23,320
On this matter,

1036
00:38:23,480 --> 00:38:25,560
you really haven't thought it through.

1037
00:38:25,760 --> 00:38:26,560
We can...

1038
00:38:26,880 --> 00:38:28,720
From the very beginning, Dayazhai

1039
00:38:28,720 --> 00:38:30,160
has been using my designs

1040
00:38:30,160 --> 00:38:32,080
for production and sales.

1041
00:38:32,200 --> 00:38:34,080
Yes, I licensed them to Dayazhai,

1042
00:38:34,600 --> 00:38:36,160
but ours isn't an exclusive partnership.

1043
00:38:36,160 --> 00:38:37,840
Xuan Bao'er is my creation,

1044
00:38:37,840 --> 00:38:39,160
like my own child.

1045
00:38:39,160 --> 00:38:40,480
And my child's future

1046
00:38:40,840 --> 00:38:42,480
is something I have to think about.

1047
00:38:46,360 --> 00:38:47,160
Fine.

1048
00:38:49,080 --> 00:38:51,080
Then I wish you every success.

1049
00:38:58,480 --> 00:38:59,880
I will definitely succeed.

1050
00:39:04,480 --> 00:39:05,200
Xuan Yan!

1051
00:39:11,000 --> 00:39:11,800
Chairman,

1052
00:39:11,800 --> 00:39:12,720
I think we can still

1053
00:39:12,720 --> 00:39:13,240
discuss this in another meeting.

1054
00:39:13,240 --> 00:39:13,920
Meeting adjourned.

1055
00:39:14,160 --> 00:39:14,760
Chairman, please just...

1056
00:39:14,760 --> 00:39:15,360
Adjourned!

1057
00:39:20,040 --> 00:39:21,280
What are you all still standing around for?

1058
00:39:21,280 --> 00:39:22,640
Go on, get out, get out.

1059
00:39:22,800 --> 00:39:23,560
Dismissed.

1060
00:39:44,000 --> 00:39:44,800
Sister Xin.

1061
00:39:45,400 --> 00:39:47,680
Xuan Yan actually dared to challenge the chairman in public.

1062
00:39:47,760 --> 00:39:49,160
Has he lost his mind?

1063
00:39:50,440 --> 00:39:52,200
What are we supposed to do now?

1064
00:39:54,320 --> 00:39:55,200
I don't know.

1065
00:39:56,520 --> 00:39:58,360
I think Xuan Yan is finished.

1066
00:39:59,240 --> 00:40:00,640
And we're finished too.

1067
00:40:08,720 --> 00:40:10,040
Xuan Yan, Xuan Yan, wait up.

1068
00:40:12,080 --> 00:40:14,440
Xuan Yan, do you even see me as a friend?

1069
00:40:14,800 --> 00:40:16,280
It's because I see you as a friend

1070
00:40:16,280 --> 00:40:17,560
that I didn't tell you beforehand.

1071
00:40:17,560 --> 00:40:18,640
Just listen to me.

1072
00:40:18,640 --> 00:40:20,560
Hold off on the cooperative for now.

1073
00:40:20,560 --> 00:40:21,760
Give me a little time.

1074
00:40:21,760 --> 00:40:23,400
Let me go persuade the chairman, okay?

1075
00:40:23,400 --> 00:40:25,760
Why does your chairman have to be persuaded?

1076
00:40:26,600 --> 00:40:28,480
I already gave your chairman his chance.

1077
00:40:28,560 --> 00:40:29,880
Different paths, no shared plans.

1078
00:40:29,960 --> 00:40:31,640
His arrogance is nothing but stupidity to me.

1079
00:40:31,640 --> 00:40:32,640
Then could you

1080
00:40:32,880 --> 00:40:34,440
also think about me a little?

1081
00:40:34,440 --> 00:40:36,560
If working here is too hard on you,

1082
00:40:37,040 --> 00:40:38,480
the general manager position at the cooperative

1083
00:40:38,480 --> 00:40:39,560
will always be waiting for you.

1084
00:40:40,600 --> 00:40:41,400
Xuan Yan.

1085
00:40:42,040 --> 00:40:43,760
I'm saying all this for your own good.

1086
00:40:44,080 --> 00:40:44,880
Thanks.

1087
00:40:46,480 --> 00:40:47,360
Just wish me luck.

1088
00:41:09,240 --> 00:41:10,080
Chairman.

1089
00:41:10,240 --> 00:41:11,640
I'll do my best to talk sense into Ms. Xin.

1090
00:41:11,920 --> 00:41:14,080
I'm sure the Xuan Yan matter can be resolved.

1091
00:41:14,080 --> 00:41:16,920
That contract you signed with Xuan Yan...

1092
00:41:17,640 --> 00:41:19,240
it's an absolute humiliation.

1093
00:41:21,520 --> 00:41:23,080
I agree it shouldn't have been signed like that.

1094
00:41:23,360 --> 00:41:25,520
But Ms. Xin values loyalty above all.

1095
00:41:25,840 --> 00:41:27,240
When it comes to the company's interests,

1096
00:41:27,240 --> 00:41:28,640
she doesn't think it through enough.

1097
00:41:39,920 --> 00:41:40,720
Yuqing.

1098
00:41:41,640 --> 00:41:42,400
I can tell.

1099
00:41:43,360 --> 00:41:45,080
You're a thoughtful one.

1100
00:41:46,360 --> 00:41:47,200
Chairman,

1101
00:41:47,680 --> 00:41:49,120
Dayazhai is my home.

1102
00:41:52,640 --> 00:41:53,920
You have my number.

1103
00:41:54,360 --> 00:41:56,920
If Xin Ran makes any move,

1104
00:41:57,400 --> 00:41:58,720
contact me immediately.

1105
00:42:00,040 --> 00:42:00,880
I will.

1106
00:42:17,920 --> 00:42:19,720
Today, Brother Min gathered everyone here

1107
00:42:20,280 --> 00:42:21,560
not really for this boat,

1108
00:42:22,040 --> 00:42:22,880
but for

1109
00:42:23,160 --> 00:42:24,880
the co-op's boat.

1110
00:42:25,640 --> 00:42:26,720
What kind of boat is that?

1111
00:42:28,400 --> 00:42:29,080
Let's do this.

1112
00:42:29,080 --> 00:42:30,440
Let me ask you all a question.

1113
00:42:30,640 --> 00:42:32,800
Do you think Dayazhai makes money?

1114
00:42:33,200 --> 00:42:33,880
Does that even need saying?

1115
00:42:33,880 --> 00:42:35,440
Does Dayazhai need to make money?

1116
00:42:35,520 --> 00:42:37,040
Their paper-printing machines

1117
00:42:37,040 --> 00:42:38,560
aren't printing paper anymore,

1118
00:42:38,560 --> 00:42:40,240
they're printing banknotes, cash.

1119
00:42:40,640 --> 00:42:40,960
Exactly.

1120
00:42:40,960 --> 00:42:43,520
Isn't that plain for everyone to see?

1121
00:42:43,520 --> 00:42:44,520
In my whole life,

1122
00:42:44,520 --> 00:42:46,520
if I could earn just a fraction of Dayazhai's,

1123
00:42:46,800 --> 00:42:47,280
I'd be satisfied.

1124
00:42:48,240 --> 00:42:49,840
Yes, Dayazhai is making money.

1125
00:42:50,080 --> 00:42:51,000
But what they earn

1126
00:42:51,160 --> 00:42:52,440
is from online sales.

